festival.introText:
The Gathering Fest returns to Meridian Showground in Cleethorpes on Saturday 10th June 2023. Featuring: 5 Arenas, 60 Acts, Food & Stalls, VIP Arena and 12 Hours of Music. 

 

The Gathering Fest is a 5,000 capacity annual Dance Festival that takes place in Cleethorpes. 5 Arenas, Over 60 International DJs & Live Acts, Food & Stalls, VIP Arena, across 12 Hours.
festival.descriptionText: Skiddle is an official ticket outlet of The Gathering Fest 2023. Get The Gathering Fest tickets, news and information with Skiddle.com
festival.location: Meridian Showground in North East Lincolnsh

reviews.title: Review of The Gathering Fest 2022
reviews.body: if u asked me the day after and not s month after I probably could of answered your question  but my trainers had a gud time and a pie lost he's literally danced he's feet off big up to the gathering crew

reviews.title: Review of The Gathering Fest 2022
reviews.body: Great day, shame again about the drinks situation. Only in small print did it say you had to use your vouchers by 10.30. Lost about 30, lots of other people in the same boat, very disappointing. Also lager was Coors Light which tastes like water yet charged at a high price. Please sort the drinks out, only thing negative about the event now.

reviews.title: Review of The Gathering Fest 2022
reviews.body: I don't like it when they don't display the line up before entry. I was told by promoters that set times would be displayed at the bar but they wasn't. To find set times lanyards had to be purchased which is a rip off!

faqs.question: How much are The Gathering Fest tickets?
faqs.answer: Keep an eye on the ticket area for prices.

faqs.question: When is The Gathering Fest 2023?
faqs.answer: The Gathering Fest takes place on Saturday 10th June 2023.

faqs.question: Disabled Access Information
faqs.answer: Disabled toilets available on site. The site is all flat ground & easy to manoeuvre. Queue jump will be provided for any wheelchair users, please make yourself know to staff on the day.

faqs.question: Are pre-payment plan tickets available?
faqs.answer: Yes Payment Plan tickets are available so you can spread the cost of your ticket over multiple smaller payments.

faqs.question: What happens If I bought a ticket and cannot attend?
faqs.answer:
Unfortunately we can’t issue you with a refund if you can’t make the event due to work commitments or your mates have dropped out. In these circumstances, we advise passing on your tickets privately to avoid losing out on the money spent.

Refunds can only be offered if the event is cancelled or postponed, as agreed upon purchase.
